data.description: You are not going to believe this recent remodel. From top to bottom, everything has been done for you. Now, you just have to move in. Newer flooring throughout the downstairs and newer carpet for the upstairs loft bedroom. This cabin has a newer metal roof, ceilings, fixtures and paint throughout. Great insulation makes this cabin easy to heat and cool. Front porch has new railings and the low-maintenance back and side yards have new privacy fencing. Just 15 minutes from the Branson landing. Great home at an affordable price.
